<p>看了这么多写实的电影海报之后，是不是觉得很震撼？</p>
<p>态爷除了擅长这种冲击性强、画面感丰富的画风以外，萌萌哒的画风也是不在话下~~</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="热搜刷屏、央视推荐，这样一位神仙插画师，已经给大家请来了！" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-388735" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ty-hand-painted-1-20200914-44.jpg" width="750" height="750" /></span> <span class="img-zoom"><img alt="热搜刷屏、央视推荐，这样一位神仙插画师，已经给大家请来了！" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-388743" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ty-hand-painted-1-20200914-52.jpg" width="750" height="750" /></span> <span class="img-zoom"><img alt="热搜刷屏、央视推荐，这样一位神仙插画师，已经给大家请来了！" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-388742" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ty-hand-painted-1-20200914-51.jpg" width="750" height="750" /></span> <span class="img-zoom"><img alt="热搜刷屏、央视推荐，这样一位神仙插画师，已经给大家请来了！" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-388741" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ty-hand-painted-1-20200914-50.jpg" width="750" height="750" /></span> <span class="img-zoom"><img alt="热搜刷屏、央视推荐，这样一位神仙插画师，已经给大家请来了！" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-388740" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ty-hand-painted-1-20200914-49.jpg" width="750" height="750" /></span> <span class="img-zoom"><img alt="热搜刷屏、央视推荐，这样一位神仙插画师，已经给大家请来了！" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-388739" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ty-hand-painted-1-20200914-48.jpg" width="750" height="750" /></span> <span class="img-zoom"><img alt="热搜刷屏、央视推荐，这样一位神仙插画师，已经给大家请来了！" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-388738" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ty-hand-painted-1-20200914-47.jpg" width="750" height="750" /></span> <span class="img-zoom"><img alt="热搜刷屏、央视推荐，这样一位神仙插画师，已经给大家请来了！" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-388737" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ty-hand-painted-1-20200914-46.jpg" width="750" height="750" /></span> <span class="img-zoom"><img alt="热搜刷屏、央视推荐，这样一位神仙插画师，已经给大家请来了！" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-388736" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ty-hand-painted-1-20200914-45.jpg" width="750" height="750" /></span></p>
<p>这种温暖可爱的画风，爱了爱了~~~</p>
<p>而对于新粉而言，提起态爷，他们会很兴奋的说：「是不是那个超厉害的听说系列的作者！」</p>
<p>「听说系列」是态爷最近非常火爆的系列教程，也被网友调侃称作「听说你啥都不会」。转发最高达到了 6w7，让态爷在微博的人气迅速飙升。如果你还没有看过，一定一定去微博补一下这些超级大干货：</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="热搜刷屏、央视推荐，这样一位神仙插画师，已经给大家请来了！" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-388744" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ty-hand-painted-1-20200914-53.jpg" width="750" height="660" /></span></p>
